metadata.name: moon and back
metadata.description:
Moon and back was hand drawn by PHRAZE for someone you love. (That someone can be you.) 

Sound on for max love. 

A simple rocket travels from the earth to the moon and back again with an infinitely looping (and infinity shaped) orbital path.  Leaving a trail of letters in its wake that spells out the words "I love you to the moon and back."

Holders of this token will have access to a high res, printable file should they choose to print it themselves.
